ON_US_ACCEPTED_APP_ACCEPTED
Business Logic:
Direct On-Us customers whose eligibility outcome was Accept, who submitted a full application, and whose final application outcome was accepted/booked.

Transformation Logic:
QUOTE_DECISION = 'Accept'
QTIND = 'F'
LINKED_APPLICATION_IDENTIFIER IS NULL
FULL_APPLICATION_STATUS_CODE = 'COMPLETE'

Journey Stage:
Direct On-Us Eligibility Outcome → Full Application Submission → Final Application Outcome

